data.description: Welcome to your home away from home! This cozy cabin is nestled on 17.5 acres of picturesque natural beauty. There is not a bad view in the house or from the gorgeous wraparound porch that is ready for coffee drinking, star gazing or just relaxing in a rocking chair. As you walk into this rustic, yet upscale charmer, you'll notice the vaulted ceilings, exposed beams and tons of natural light. A hand carved bar and a stone fireplace are just two of the features that make this open concept living room unique and inviting. The  kitchen includes granite countertops and an abundance of storage space and breakfast bar. Two bedrooms and a quaint loft area provide a spacious area for rest and relaxation. As you journey outside, you'll find a detached 2 car garage offers plenty of storage space for all the toys and hunting gear! This stunning outdoor space will delight family and friends for years to come!
